  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Slashvival is a third-person action RPG with roguelite elements. Use swords to fight mutant creatures in a medieval low-poly world. Survive intense battles and rescue your family in this thrilling hack-and-slash adventure!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990410/extras/7af715f7de769fc6e05a45d2965087d1.avif?t=1759584139\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990410/extras/22bd2013e48ecf229e4f634de4e575f9.poster.avif?t=1759584139\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990410/extras/22bd2013e48ecf229e4f634de4e575f9.webm?t=1759584139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990410/extras/22bd2013e48ecf229e4f634de4e575f9.mp4?t=1759584139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Slashvival</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slashvival offers an intense survival experience in a medieval fantasy world where every day brings a new challenge. Face procedurally generated enemies, unpredictable climates, and scarce resources as you fight to protect your family.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990410/extras/f822f76eb8a945ee3e384684359b6653.poster.avif?t=1759584139\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990410/extras/f822f76eb8a945ee3e384684359b6653.webm?t=1759584139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990410/extras/f822f76eb8a945ee3e384684359b6653.mp4?t=1759584139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in epic battles against powerful bosses, upgrade your character's abilities, and discover new strategies with each playthrough. With a blend of rogue-lite mechanics and hack-and-slash combat, Slashvival provides endless replayability and excitement in a low-poly environment. Survive the night, and face whatever the next day brings.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Slashvival is a third-person action RPG with roguelite elements. Use swords to fight mutant creatures in a medieval low-poly world. Survive intense battles and rescue your family in this thrilling hack-and-slash adventure!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990410/extras/7af715f7de769fc6e05a45d2965087d1.avif?t=1759584139\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990410/extras/22bd2013e48ecf229e4f634de4e575f9.poster.avif?t=1759584139\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990410/extras/22bd2013e48ecf229e4f634de4e575f9.webm?t=1759584139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990410/extras/22bd2013e48ecf229e4f634de4e575f9.mp4?t=1759584139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Slashvival</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slashvival offers an intense survival experience in a medieval fantasy world where every day brings a new challenge. Face procedurally generated enemies, unpredictable climates, and scarce resources as you fight to protect your family.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990410/extras/f822f76eb8a945ee3e384684359b6653.poster.avif?t=1759584139\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990410/extras/f822f76eb8a945ee3e384684359b6653.webm?t=1759584139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990410/extras/f822f76eb8a945ee3e384684359b6653.mp4?t=1759584139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in epic battles against powerful bosses, upgrade your character's abilities, and discover new strategies with each playthrough. With a blend of rogue-lite mechanics and hack-and-slash combat, Slashvival provides endless replayability and excitement in a low-poly environment. Survive the night, and face whatever the next day brings.</p>",
